title: 12/23/21 DPS Hour 1 Brady Quinn

description:
In Hour 1 of the Dan Patrick show the crew starts with NBA Covid protocols and bringing up players. Which NFL team should stick with their QBs. Brady Quinn then joins the show to talk being cut and his take on which NFL teams should keep their QBs & NCAAF.
